OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA partly
OL,6,Fcloudy and dry evening for much of the
OL,7,Fregion. Cloud builds for coastal areas
OL,8,Fbut remaining clear inland and staying
OL,9,Fdry. Winds remaining light and
OL,10,Fvariable.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FPartly cloudy to start but
OL,13,Fremaining dry across the region.
OL,14,FMostly sunny through the late
OL,15,Fafternoon and into the evening. Winds
OL,16,Fremaining light. Temperatures
OL,17,Fgenerally average or slightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
